episodes.synopsis: After setting up camp, the team ventures into the jungle in search of two rare and threatened species: the clouded leopard and the Borneo gibbon.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Parasites and humidity plague the scientists searching for jungle elephants, while their mountaineering colleagues are lost in an isolated area.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: On a search for endangered orangutans, the team encounters a giant python, and a deadly coral snake strikes one team member.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Tara and her team search for the lost caves of Sangkulirang in the Marang Mountains, while Steve and Justine head west to the Mulu Mountains.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Steve and his colleagues attempt a daring descent through the sinkhole in the middle of a mountain into an enormous chasm known as Solo.
episodes.title: Episode 5

video.title: Expedition Borneo
video.synopsis: A team of six explorers are dropped into one of the most remote and biologically rich places on Earth to study its fragile ecosystem.
